# 📰 Indian News Hub

A modern news website built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript that fetches the latest news articles using NewsAPI.

## 🚀 Live Demo

🔗 View Website

## ✨ Features

- Latest news updates
- Search news by keyword
- Category-based navigation
- Responsive design
- Dynamic news cards
- API integration with NewsAPI

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- NewsAPI

## 📂 Project Structure

- index.html
- style.css
- script.js
- assets/

